  "prompt": "What are some suggested heart touching (English) love songs?",
  "response": "Certainly! There are many beautiful and heartfelt English love songs that resonate deeply with listeners. Here are some suggestions:\n\n1. **\"Make You Feel My Love\" by Adele / Bob Dylan**\n2. **\"Perfect\" by Ed Sheeran**\n3. **\"All of Me\" by John Legend**\n4. **\"Thinking Out Loud\" by Ed Sheeran**\n5. **\"I Will Always Love You\" by Whitney Houston / Dolly Parton**\n6. **\"Unchained Melody\" by The Righteous Brothers**\n7. **\"Endless Love\" by Lionel Richie & Diana Ross**\n8. **\"Just the Way You Are\" by Bruno Mars**\n9. **\"A Thousand Years\" by Christina Perri**\n10. **\"Your Song\" by Elton John**\n11. **\"My Heart Will Go On\" by Celine Dion**\n12. **\"I Don't Want to Miss a Thing\" by Aerosmith**\n13. **\"Have I Told You Lately\" by Rod Stewart / Van Morrison**\n14. **\"You Are So Beautiful\" by Joe Cocker**\n15. **\"Wonderful Tonight\" by Eric Clapton**\n\nThese songs are known for their poignant lyrics, soulful melodies, and the ability to evoke strong emotions connected to love and romance. Enjoy listening!",
